// *********************************************
// Specifying Tenant Definition In Your Component
// *********************************************

Create Tenant Data
==================
- create a seed data file called data/TenantData.xml
- order the tenant data respectively following:
  * Tenant
  * TenantComponent
  * TenantDataSource (org.ofbiz)
  * TenantDataSource (org.ofbiz.olap)
- specific the seed data file in a ofbiz-component.xml file following:
  
  ...
  ...
  <entity-resource type="data" reader-name="tenant" loader="main" location="data/TenantData.xml"/>
  ...
  ...

Specific Demo Reader
====================
- create a demo reader file called data/DemoLoadData.txt
- enter a line for the reader, for example, seed,seed-initial,demo,ext-demo

Install Data
============
Using an Ant command to install the tenant data.

./ant run-install-readers -Ddata-readers=seed,seed-initial,tenant,demo,ext-demo

** NOTE: there will be some error logs from PostgreSQL's JDBC in the terminal but they do NOT cause any problems.
